data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION!  This Beautiful 3 Level Single Family Is Ready To Be Yours! The home is 3,300 Sq Ft of Finished Living Space Comes With A Ton of Upgrades. The Family Room Is Spacious With A Gas Fireplace/Mantel, Granite Countertops W/ Stainless Steel Appliances, Hardwood Floors Throughout The Entire 1st Level, Digital Sound System, And An Intercom System.  The Primary Bedroom Is Spacious And The Bathroom Has A Lovely Soaking Tub, Shower, And Separate Toilet Space . There Are 3 Additional Bedrooms On The Upper Level And A Huge Loft/Bonus Room. The Lower Level Has A Fully Finished Basement, Utility Room With An Abundance Of Storage, Full Bath And An Additional 5th Bedroom Or Office Space.  The Home Has A Walk Out Basement Leading To A Large Backyard. HOA Amenities Include Trash/Recycle Pickup, Snow Removal, And Maintenance Of The Common Grounds. The Musket Ridge Subdivision Is Just Minutes Away From Shopping, Restaurants And So Much More!   The Home is Priced To Sell!!
